{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"1089-bunty-na-bubbly","title":"Bunty na Bubbly ","description":"Bunty anapenda kucheza lakini hapendi sabuni na anakataa kujisafisha. Usiku mmoja anaota ndoto kuhusu viini vya uchafu. Je, ndoto yake itafanikisha yeye kubadili msimamo wake kuhusu kujiosha?","language":"Kiswahili","langCode":"sw","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["African Storybook Initiative"],"illustrators":["Sorit Gupto"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/1089-bunty-na-bubbly"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/720260/size3/bfaca307e321a40d4fce0bf9bade9047.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/720260/size6/bfaca307e321a40d4fce0bf9bade9047.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13505/size6/9907217108246f4eb01c1ac7f252464b.jpg","text":"Bunty na Bubbly\nBunty anapenda kucheza na vipepeo…\n2/12","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13506/size6/3cfef50c731271c06bc7df15adfad696.jpg","text":"… na ndege.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13507/size6/0b2cc2ad4ba1e7c14ab8f85d1cc92a02.jpg","text":"Anapenda kucheza na mashua iliyotengenezwa kutoka kwa makaratasi.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13508/size6/1fea81780050ff2039ff47dedfb38216.jpg","text":"Anapendelea pia kutengeneza mangome kutumia changarawe.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13509/size6/b4b058041a0f8816ef576bb510e2a358.jpg","text":"Bunty anaporudi nyumbani, mamake humuuliza ajisafishe.\nLakini hukataa.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13510/size6/f13b791f09d8c65688476d9d6782ede2.jpg","text":"“Nachukia sabuni!” yeye hulia.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13511/size6/45170485855b821bd3a27a6917664b6f.jpg","text":"Usiku mmoja, alikuwa na ndoto.\nAliota kuwa vijidudu vinavyosababisha magonjwa vilikuwa vimeizunguka ngome yake na vilikuwa vinamvamia.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13512/size6/05cc5eb1bd0a44d4e01e16ad4432d8fd.jpg","text":"Bunty anafukuzwa na vijidudu.\nAnakimbia kuokoa uhai wake huku akipiga mayowe, “Nisaidie…Nisaidie!”","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13513/size6/c3075a8fd3d40bc48a3983ac434329a7.jpg","text":"Ghafla, Mfalme Sabuni kwa jina Bubbly anatokezea. “Bunty, usiogope,” anasema.\n“Nenda mkavamie vijidudu!” Mfalme Sabuni anaamrisha jeshi lake la povu.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13514/size6/9e0c56e80240c4c4448a07ac8d9e80c0.jpg","text":"Jeshi la povu linafukuzia mbali vijidudu.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13515/size6/342fa90cc8f644b89f8b05984faab025.jpg","text":"Siku hizi, Bunty hupendelea kutumia sabuni, na hujipangusa na kujisugua hadi anakuwa msafi.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":106}}